Fireman Xu Weiguo grabbed the woman's arm just in time after she threatened to jump . 
  The woman was depressed after being dumped by her boyfriend and was trying to throw herself off a 10-storey tower block in Shanghai . 
  Police had failed to convince her to climb back into a nearby apartment . 
  Xu climbed out of the window and grabbed her arm just as she was about to jump  . 
  He and a colleague then helped to pull the woman back to safety . 
 